### ======================================================
### MERCADO PAGO — OAuth vendedor + webhooks (referência)
### ======================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@subscriberToken = REPLACE_SUBSCRIBER_JWT
@mpSignature = REPLACE_X_SIGNATURE_HEX

### Iniciar OAuth (JWT) — abrir mercadoPago.authorizationUrl no browser
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/mercadopago/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### Callback é chamado pelo MP no browser (público) — não invocar manualmente aqui
# GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/mercadopago/callback?code=...&state=...

### Credenciais manuais (alternativa ao OAuth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/mercadopago/manual-credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "REPLACE_MP_ACCESS_TOKEN",
  "publicKey": "REPLACE_MP_PUBLIC_KEY"
}

### Webhook assinatura plataforma (corpo real do MP + header x-signature)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/mercadopago/subscription
x-signature: {{mpSignature}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment",
  "data": { "id": "123456789" }
}

### Webhook reservas
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/reservations/mercadopago
x-signature: {{mpSignature}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment",
  "data": { "id": "123456789" }
}

### Desautorização OAuth (sem HMAC; payload típico MP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/mercadopago/deauthorization
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "application.deauthorized",
  "user_id": "123456789"
}
